longBusinessSummary: GTA Financecorp Inc. does not have any significant business operations. Previously, the company was engaged in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties in Canada. The company was formerly known as GTA Resources and Mining Inc. and changed its name to GTA Financecorp Inc. in March 2019. GTA Financecorp Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Burlington, Canada.
